---
description: Editorial grid design system and zero-diff rule for UI edits.
globs:
  - "app/**/*.tsx"
  - "components/**/*.tsx"
  - "app/styles/**/*.css"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Preserve the current layout unless the request explicitly changes behavior or copy.
- Read `DESIGN.md`, `AGENTS.md`, and `UI_CHANGE_PROTOCOL.md` before making UI edits.
- This project uses the editorial grid system: structured lines, rigid spacing, and shared layout contracts.
- Prefer changing shared rules in the owning stylesheet/component instead of patching one-off overrides.
- Generated artifacts are not part of the design system. Never edit `.next`, `.next 2`, caches, or traces.
